---
title: Quick Pork & Saucy Leek Fusilli with Garlic-Parmesan Pangrattato
description: In this dish, we've teamed a rich tomato-based sauce with leek and tender pork mince for a speedy weeknight meal that looks
and smells every bit as good as it tastes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-leek-fusilli-602a0a71.jpg
